# [[mumbo-jumbo|Mumbo-jumbo]]; obscure language or [[technicality|technicalities]]; [[jargon]]. {{defdate|from 19th c.}}
#: ''I don’t know all the theoretical '''abracadabra''' about how it works, I’m only its pilot.''
